Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:10.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:12.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My life was too short.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:15.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My head is caved in.\NMy brains are leaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:17.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end for Gion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know how to go easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:26.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A-are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:27.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:29.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:30.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:33.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:36.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:42.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:47.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean to pry,\Nbut what's your relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:51.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's repaying a debt with his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:52.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just bought a piece of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:57.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I, Ayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:03.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, he belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:07.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time you lay a hand\Non him without permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:10.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...just know you'll wind up\Nat the bottom of Tokyo Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:13.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:18.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if you're not careful,\Nyou could be fish food too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:19.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:23.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you recently confiscate\Na certain master-tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:26.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...for payback on a debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:28.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:31.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever heard the name Yoshizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:36.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an entrepreneur who runs\Na club in Roppongi as a front.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:40.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It turns out that tape\Nwas stolen from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:44.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going crazy trying\Nto get that tape back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:46.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:47.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time before...\NGion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:49.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be more concerned!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:53.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a beef with you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:08:55.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got good sources!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:58.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you knew where\Nthe tape came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You got guts, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:03.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshizumi....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:06.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gotten carried\Naway just because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:08.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...he's got some\Npoliticians as backers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:12.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He was pretty arrogant\Nwhen he tried to hired me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:15.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I will hand it to\Nhim for recognizing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:17.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...my talents as a cameraman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:19.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cameraman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:22.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's his connection to Mr. Kanoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:23.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's his connection to Mr. Kanoh?\NI don't like the way he operates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:25.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like the way he operates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:29.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So when I told him I only\Nwork with subjects I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:32.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...he got nasty with me.\NIt was horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:36.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the model they had\Nwas as good-looking as Aya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:38.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...I might have taken it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:40.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:44.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are adult movies\Nthat aren't that hard-core.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:48.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure you look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:49.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,S-stop kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.28,0:09:50.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gion...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:54.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding, just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:56.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:57.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:09:59.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:02.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:04.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:11.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you would do anything if\Nyou didn't have to sleep with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:13.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hooking you up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...with a lucrative job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:19.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask and you shall receive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to shoot\Na cutie like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:25.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...is a cameraman's\Ndream come true, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:27.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...is what I'd like\Nto be saying, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:30.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I have to decline, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:31.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aya doesn't seem\Nto be down with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:37.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's an adult movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:41.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...but there has to be love in\Nthe sex scenes. That's my policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:44.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Gion...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:47.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't quite understand\Nthe situation, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:49.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...you should be nicer to Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:52.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please excuse me.\NShut up you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:59.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and do as I\Nsay before I lose it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:01.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:04.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go right away to\Nget my equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, is he serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:13.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:16.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:20.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the\NLoan shark from Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:22.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:25.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand you have\Nsomething of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:26.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:28.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A master-tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:30.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:33.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever heard the name Yoshizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:37.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It turns out that tape\Nwas stolen from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:45.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be in your best\Ninterest to return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:50.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be sorry if you\Nmake an enemy of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Gion did...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:59.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear he's your kid brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a stupid kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:08.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want\Nto end up like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:13.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what\Nyou're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:21.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember meeting\Na third rate club owner...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:22.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...from the outskirts of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:24.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw with me kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:34.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:35.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:37.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:38.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on!\NAre you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:39.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:42.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I'm sorry!\NI'll clean it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:12:59.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:03.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can get your Loan shark\Npermit revoked in an instant...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:14.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:22.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough barking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:26.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you messing with\Na kid like me, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:31.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You came all this way from\NRoppongi to make a fool of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:35.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to grow up\Nto be like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:37.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:40.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:40.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!\NSir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:46.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're disturbing\Nthe other customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:47.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:49.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the perpetrator here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:54.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, sir. We were remiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:00.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sorry to have\Ncaused the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready to go to our room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:06.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...\NAyase...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:10.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't piss me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:15.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:17.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know who you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:20.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...Yoshizumi, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:25.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't forget, this is Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:31.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not wise to wage\Na war against him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:36.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,For your own sake, please, leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:55.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:57.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:12.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no different than\Nany other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:17.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It turns you on to be\Nwatched, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:21.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:25.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You loved it when we had\Nsex in front of the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:26.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:28.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:30.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was disgusted...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:31.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:33.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:37.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to\Nremind you what you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:42.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...let me come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:49.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:54.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...say it because I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you ask them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:59.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who will be watching\Nthis video we're about to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:00.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:02.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means\Nto make an adult movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:10.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm eager to see who will watch\Nthe numerous copies we circulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:13.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You might not be able\Nto go back to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:15.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:20.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of this man,\Nit's all falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:23.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you leave school...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:26.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...this video will haunt you\Nfor the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:30.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My life, my morals...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:33.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...my self, my body, my soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:37.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:38.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:41.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:44.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I get out\Nof this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:48.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:50.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd still rather\Nnot sleep with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:07.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:12.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:13.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:16.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:21.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:22.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:24.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.14,0:17:31.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:41.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:44.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:48.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:53.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's\Nwrong with Mr. Kanoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he look so pained?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:02.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,After what he's said to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:09.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I feel so\Ntender towards him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:13.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The video's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to Gion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:17.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:20.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:23.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come get you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:42.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is coming\Napart because of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:47.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My life, my morals,\Nmy body, my soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:53.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:59.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he seem so kind to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:10.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:20.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come get you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:23.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:26.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...I tell him I wanted\Nto go home with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:29.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never find the words...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...and so I never say what I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:34.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I going to lose him too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:41.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd become my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:46.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:49.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:52.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:02.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:05.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshizumi! I told you\Nnot to be rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:09.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you kidnapping this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Aya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:13.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Gion...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:16.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are my bait\Nto lure Kanoh out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:18.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Blame it on Kanoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:20.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's misplaced resentment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:23.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got a gripe,\Ntell it to the person...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:26.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...who stole the tape from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:27.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:30.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea what he's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:34.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Somuku Kanoh is not the\Nkind of man who will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:37.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...come running because\Nyou have his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:38.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:39.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait all you want!\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:50.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, he's not even\Nremotely concerned about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:54.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Do you get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:00.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go, Yoshizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:04.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mr. Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:08.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to use my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:10.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:12.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:17.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing compared\Nto what Bro does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:22.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, a hostage\Nmeans nothing to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the kid go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:24.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the kid go.\NI can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:25.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:29.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:31.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:33.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:36.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.99,0:21:38.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, you\Npervert politician!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:41.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell your\Ndaughter and your voters!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:44.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to need\Nyour help, Gion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:45.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:49.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanoh's kid brother\Nis going to film...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:52.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...his little lover being violated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:53.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a great idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:55.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:58.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can lick your wounds later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:00.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready to film!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:01.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:02.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:07.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:10.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,As promised, we won't\Nshow your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.06,0:22:14.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to give\Nme the master-tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:16.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:23.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he's indeed his lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:26.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.38,0:22:31.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already been broken in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:35.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But his reaction is\Nso naive, it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.98,0:22:37.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:42.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...your first time with\Nsomeone other than him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.53,0:22:46.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:52.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's\Nthe same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:22:58.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:04.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.45,0:23:07.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.42,0:23:09.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.55,0:23:11.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, let me tend to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:12.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:16.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you have no manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.92,0:23:19.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:21.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and film!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.53,0:23:24.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.60,0:23:27.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be fun\Nto discipline you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:33.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:35.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your first time\Nwith drugs like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:40.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to make you feel better.\NYou have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.18,0:23:42.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Yoshizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.62,0:23:45.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:48.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to dominate with violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:51.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But with a boy with eyes\Nas innocent as yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:57.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...I want to totally\Nhumiliate and violate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:23:58.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.80,0:24:02.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:04.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.31,0:24:06.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Gion.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:08.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said he wouldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.64,0:24:10.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.18,0:24:14.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our best customer is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.53,0:24:27.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your master?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.23,0:24:30.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring the\Nmoney and the tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.47,0:24:33.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't have come!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.70,0:24:37.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.91,0:24:40.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He came.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.04,0:24:41.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.31,0:24:43.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.61,0:24:44.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You freak politician!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.35,0:24:46.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.61,0:24:49.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to\Nkeep your filthy hands on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.28,0:24:51.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.05,0:24:53.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.32,0:24:57.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you care what\Nhappens to the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.26,0:24:59.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,On your knees, Kanoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.59,0:25:02.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on your knees and\Napologize for yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.74,0:25:10.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.51,0:25:12.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.46,0:25:37.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Mr. Kanoh! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.16,0:25:38.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.16,0:25:40.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.00,0:25:46.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rub your head on the floor\Nand say that you're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.48,0:25:49.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.24,0:25:51.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.85,0:25:55.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had said that I wanted\Nto go home with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.35,0:25:56.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This wouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.18,0:25:59.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanoh, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.89,0:26:01.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.09,0:26:05.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said my hands were filthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.46,0:26:07.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...but what about yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.63,0:26:09.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you to do to\Nthis kid with those hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.96,0:26:12.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so different about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.90,0:26:15.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.70,0:26:17.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.27,0:26:18.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.51,0:26:20.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.87,0:26:21.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.78,0:26:24.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanoh is...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.68,0:26:28.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.92,0:26:30.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now or never!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.45,0:26:33.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.39,0:26:35.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanoh is...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.73,0:26:40.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,See you...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.26,0:26:45.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanoh was kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.93,0:26:47.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He was...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.57,0:26:56.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.11,0:26:59.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you check the goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.38,0:27:00.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.75,0:27:02.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.78,0:27:04.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't go\Nthinking this is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.75,0:27:08.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You will never\Ndisobey me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.29,0:27:13.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Gion!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.36,0:27:14.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.00,0:27:16.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The weight of $6,300.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.66,0:27:20.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how stupid are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.93,0:27:23.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we have to re-discipline another idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.70,0:27:24.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we have to re-discipline another idiot.\NYeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.94,0:27:27.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you'll be first, Yoshizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.34,0:27:30.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you, you freak politician.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.04,0:27:33.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.85,0:27:40.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-you...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.32,0:27:41.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let my daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.29,0:27:46.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...who you started a war with!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.64,0:28:04.08,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,When I opened the window\Nand spoke to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.14,0:28:10.55,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...I could see that the\Nwintry, night sky was sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.68,0:28:16.35,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the emotions\Nof all the people everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.42,0:28:22.95,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...had turned into those stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.16,0:28:29.97,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,That promise we made so long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.30,0:28:35.30,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...is something I still\Ncling tightly to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.61,0:28:44.68,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,On sleepless nights in my dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.95,0:28:53.98,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if a single tear falls...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.06,0:29:00.00,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll never forget that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.30,0:29:11.91,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved, just keep me warm forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.61,0:29:18.24,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm caught\Nin a rainfall of grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.32,0:29:25.35,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...I want to become your love.
